{"tid":398033,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試左東海堂個抺茶流心月餅？","createTime":"2017-09-13T01:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T07:50:52.000Z","uid":30895,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c71a2eb39909437328115d491774029a55357c0","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T01:30:14.000Z","msg":"屌你老味真係勁撚難食！<br />\n一開始見佢啲廣告又幾吸引所以同女朋友夾份一人買一盒返屋企（兩盒平啲）<br />\n點知尋日終於攞到，第一印象係個盒都幾靚，但係一打開，啲月餅仲細撚過冰皮月餅。<br />\n幾鳩百年前，啲人用月餅嚟傳紙仔，你將啲餡轉做流心都不在話下，仲要咁撚細粒！無晒月餅呢感覺啦！最嬲係連冰皮月餅都大撚過你呀！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n講味道，又唔係好食，直頭可以算得上係難食！<br />\n個餅皮又林又油，咬落去無香味，加埋個餅本身有少少抺茶味，可以話係臭！餅餡普遍係用綠豆蓉，呢個冚家鏟就加左杏仁！搞到成個餅嘅配搭極之奇怪！然後又多油，肥林林。最後食到個心，啲抺茶終於流出嚟，仲要唔多！我本身其實係好鍾意食抺茶先至比面買盒試下，如果唔係我寧願食傳統月餅跟住糖尿同膽固醇爆炸都開心過食呢件垃圾！如果唔係鍾意食抺茶嘅人，會覺得呢個月餅又苦又臭到仆街！<br />\n<br />\n屌好嬲！推到大家見到我篇文唔好去買佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858dce0ecc7733f85621e6449fa26e880fc5bcb5","tid":398033,"uid":89259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T01:33:03.000Z","msg":"有無圖"},{"pid":"f3be7eaf848216307e38d7653593215956267c25","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:22:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無圖</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/102140_96a0a7d33b5523cbcb30835c1df15506.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F102140_96a0a7d33b5523cbcb30835c1df15506.jpg&h=1485f863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/102211_28ed55ae14731225fa8a499e40515bab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F102211_28ed55ae14731225fa8a499e40515bab.jpg&h=d247e08c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11db3e82ab2086f98d9983f50c0bba142569adfb","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:24:24.000Z","msg":"得個盒好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ace847fdd051da524e881218e507501f7c65f1","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538f152f190a947ca53ce863483aa582bad8db24","tid":398033,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:47:41.000Z","msg":"東海堂同美心有咩關係？(7分)"},{"pid":"75fb00d8a3a3830355b547907408e55c5c1180ff","tid":398033,"uid":106278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:49:25.000Z","msg":"d人話整熱先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"