":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:37:47.000Z","msg":"做美心個陣食到唔想食"},{"pid":"376c4a2118ce7f06b977204e0acc9d35f1704216","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知係咪打手，但寫得好好笑<br />\n正皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔否認我呢篇文會引來一部份唔識呢款月餅嘅人而家知道有佢嘅存在，但我真心唔建議大家貪得意買，除非真係抹茶FANS"},{"pid":"e232e27656506e0cf01273c7b920a8c39ea8e1cf","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>東海堂同美心有咩關係？(7分)</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知喎</blockquote><br />\n同一個集團 仲有元氣 Starbucks (好似係）</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁！！<br />\n好心東海堂唔好整啲奇怪月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc07526846a037a69a2030b913bf4117f6a3694","tid":398033,"uid":1022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"而家d月餅整撚到棋子餅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd味又出到古古怪怪，仲要難食"},{"pid":"80314ee08ca1009aeae1a2d1767eef5167070fc6","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家d月餅整撚到棋子餅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd味又出到古古怪怪，仲要難食</blockquote><br />\n無撚有錯，整到好似好精緻咁，扮晒上菜<br />\n題外話，阿爸阿媽兩個人夾埋食左一舊，都表示唔鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96680364aa97095036663f237c739462911b7209","tid":398033,"uid":81876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"唔好食"},{"pid":"71b0569733c57b2ce2b0fb1184668f87d89684c3","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:45:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好食</blockquote><br />\n真食評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係得我話"},{"pid":"8c6024253769154f8fd1c051b3209e030ee4a9f2","tid":398033,"uid":1926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"食落去唔似月餅"},{"pid":"23b5d62bfc5ee12a59e51cd6442654d5e97525d4","tid":398033,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"好彩係人地公司俾我嫁姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不吃也罷"},{"pid":"47f695e74c07ff33f4fce16f0f5528fa21b08a3a","tid":398033,"uid":60095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:53:25.000Z","msg":"伏已中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614de9d51fcfee39b1e5191e322923057c3bc39a","tid":398033,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家d月餅整撚到棋子餅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd味又出到古古怪怪，仲要難食</blockquote><br />\n無撚有錯，整到好似好精緻咁，扮晒上菜<br />\n題外話，阿爸阿媽兩個人夾埋食左一舊，都表示唔鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係， 以前一窩蜂間間出冰皮， 明明就係糯米糍差唔多嘢扮上菜， 而家又一窩蜂出奶黃同流心， 都係食番傳統嗰啲最好食"},{"pid":"9ef15a99fd2ad197ca93bc4b1b22049d0260c558","tid":398033,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:55:01.000Z","msg":"東海堂除咗蛋糕冇嘢好食"},{"pid":"5cf2574b38bfdd4e263e6040bf9970c06e57dc69","tid":398033,"uid":40,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:56:37.000Z","msg":"東海堂樣樣嘢包裝都好靚 次次都因為樣買 成日中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888319dc17fe01efbde792ecf2a723c7b1e38f7f","tid":398033,"uid":104057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:57:35.000Z","msg":"但出面賣到斷市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb073060739ff3d8774eeaf9795512b25cf44ec","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:07:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食落去唔似月餅</blockquote><br />\n乜都唔似"},{"pid":"82ed711d3f9ff0cd8f9a36efa755ef70924af810","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但出面賣到斷市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要玩預訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6984997c606f51973752358179abe60a842ee1b4","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家d月餅整撚到棋子餅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd味又出到古古怪怪，仲要難食</blockquote><br />\n無撚有錯，整到好似好精緻咁，扮晒上菜<br />\n題外話，阿爸阿媽兩個人夾埋食左一舊，都表示唔鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係， 以前一窩蜂間間出冰皮， 明明就係糯米糍差唔多嘢扮上菜， 而家又一窩蜂出奶黃同流心， 都係食番傳統嗰啲最好食</blockquote><br />\n其實冰皮月餅我而家都覺得定位好奇怪<br />\n雖然味道係唔錯，但係真係無月餅感覺<br />\n不過講起冰皮月餅都有個通病就係太多綠豆蓉，勁少餡，整體嚟講係偏貴"},{"pid":"934a9ea0054155d6787cab9e10b70a364b32c2a8","tid":398033,"uid":13505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:12:22.000Z","msg":"東海堂只係包裝好過同檔次, 但質素同大班美心一樣係垃圾狗也不屌"},{"pid":"692132d7f0231d4da2c1cfb098ce73d2ab933a81","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東海堂樣樣嘢包裝都好靚 次次都因為樣買 成日中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢個包裝係幾靚嘅～"},{"pid":"e1da38f157ee1ec3c10af56d4373c3085d77e44d","tid":398033,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東海堂只係包裝好過同檔次, 但質素同大班美心一樣係垃圾狗也不屌</blockquote><br />\n如果係大班同美心OK啦，超碼無咁貴"},{"pid":"bf976f5118b8c97b6a757c907d24e3d9623c36c4","tid":398033,"uid":72801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:19:14.000Z","msg":"我同事話似蛋糕多過月餅"},{"pid":"c30f5c1668eb1ae8d5a437706bfbaaff6dd07976","tid":398033,"uid":39065,"like":0,"dislike":0