if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442951fb641583f245e4a8a8abc942c1d49adcdb","tid":398033,"uid":39065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食左 真係好撚難食<br />\n紫薯粟子個個還好</blockquote><br />\n屌，有紫薯栗子咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本抺茶個質地同味道就唔啱做月餅<br />\n反而紫薯同栗子成件事啱好多</blockquote><br />\n紫薯真心高質，不過更少貨<br />\n<br />\n利申唔食紫薯所以無試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae814fbf6fe36875ed744459f899e866cc69d7a","tid":398033,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"東海堂真係除左蛋糕，全部垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nD新潮月餅9成都不知所謂，之前買過紅豆抹茶同唔知咩，總之全部甜到反胃，又唔係好食既甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}